original_title: Seki A Oe: A Crazy Samoan Love Story
overview: Jack is a hopeless romantic. Angel is a down-to-Earth in-the-closet-party-goer. Jack meets Angel and it's love at first sight, but Angel rejects Jack, now it's Diana, a fiery trans-gender to the rescue! This is Seki A Oe: A Crazy Samoan Love Story.
title: Seki A Oe: A Crazy Samoan Love Story
